n in Kirchenangelegenheiten zu akzeptieren, verwarfen sie eine herkömmliche, staatlich-sanktionierte Vorgehensweise und förderten die Entwicklung einer moderneren Beziehung zwischen den Bürgern und dem Staat.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Aug 2020) 0aChurch and statezGermanyzPrussiaxHistoryy19th century. 0aLutheranszSilesiaxHistoryy19th century. 0aPolitics and culturezGermanyzPrussiaxHistoryy19th centuryvSources. 0aPolitics and culturezGermanyzPrussiaxHistoryy20th centuryvSources. 0aSocial conflictzSilesiaxHistoryy19th century. 4aAltlutheraner. 4aOld Lutherans. 4aPreußen / 19. Jahrhundert. 4aPrussia/19th century. 4aPrussian religious policy. 4aVormärz. 4alandesherrliches Kirchenregiment. 4apreußische Religionspolitik. 4aworldly rule over the church. 7aHISTORY / Modern / General.2bisacsh1 aBBAW, , eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aNeugebauer, Wolfgang, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aRathgeber, Christina, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2017z9783110547764oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831105298210 cprintz978311052943240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311053150340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110531503423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110531503.jpg  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2017  aZDB-23-DGGb2017